import { InfoCircleOutlined, UserOutlined } from "@ant-design/icons";
import { Button, Input, Tooltip } from "antd";
import {
  MainContainer,
  FirstConatiner,
  SecContainer,
  HeadingSection,
  TextSection,
  RightConatiner,
  LeftContainer,
  FirstRightConatiner,
  InputSection,
  MidSection,
  ButtonSection,
  LastSection,
  LastInputSection,
  LeftDarkContainer,
  TopTextDetails,
  MidTextDetails,
  TextInRow,
  BottomText,
  FirstText,
  SecTextForDetails,
  ButonContainer,
  BottomTextSection,
  SPlTextSection,
} from "../../styles/views/splitter";

export const SplitterView = () => {
  const tip = [
    { key: "item1", percentage: "5%", isCustom: false, isClick: true },
    { key: "item2", percentage: "5%", isCustom: false, isClick: true },
    { key: "item3", percentage: "5%", isCustom: false, isClick: true },
    { key: "item1", percentage: "5%", isCustom: false, isClick: true },
    { key: "item1", percentage: "5%", isCustom: false, isClick: true },
    { key: "item1", percentage: "5%", isCustom: false, isClick: true },
  ];
  return (
    <MainContainer>
      <FirstConatiner>
        <HeadingSection>
          <SPlTextSection>SPLT </SPlTextSection>
          <BottomTextSection>TTER</BottomTextSection>
        </HeadingSection>
      </FirstConatiner>
      <SecContainer>
        <RightConatiner>
          <FirstRightConatiner>
            <TextSection>Bill</TextSection>
            <InputSection>
              <Input placeholder="$" />
            </InputSection>
          </FirstRightConatiner>
          <MidSection>
            <TextSection>Select Tip N</TextSection>
            <ButtonSection>
              <Button type="dashed">5% </Button>
              <Button type="dashed">10%</Button>
              <Button type="dashed">15%</Button>
              <Button type="dashed">25%</Button>
              <Button type="dashed">50%</Button>
              <Button type="dashed">Custom</Button>
            </ButtonSection>
          </MidSection>
          <LastSection>
            <TextSection>Number of People</TextSection>

            <LastInputSection>
              <Input
                placeholder="Enter your username"
                prefix={<UserOutlined className="site-form-item-icon" />}
                suffix={
                  <Tooltip title="Extra information">
                    <InfoCircleOutlined style={{ color: "rgba(0,0,0,.45)" }} />
                  </Tooltip>
                }
              />
            </LastInputSection>
          </LastSection>
        </RightConatiner>
        <LeftContainer>
          <LeftDarkContainer>
            <TopTextDetails>
              <TextInRow>
                <FirstText>Tip Amount</FirstText>
                <SecTextForDetails>/Person</SecTextForDetails>
              </TextInRow>
              <BottomText>$0.0</BottomText>
            </TopTextDetails>
            <MidTextDetails>
              <TextInRow>
                <FirstText>Total</FirstText>
                <SecTextForDetails>/Person</SecTextForDetails>
              </TextInRow>
              <BottomText>$0.0</BottomText>
            </MidTextDetails>
            <ButonContainer>
              <Button>Default Button</Button>
            </ButonContainer>
          </LeftDarkContainer>
        </LeftContainer>
      </SecContainer>
    </MainContainer>
  );
};
